<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="P" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Pandarus" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Pandarus,</orth> the archetype of pimps in <bibl n="shak. tro 1.1.48" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. I, 1, 48</bibl> etc. <cit><quote>shall I Sir P. of Troy become?</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 1.3.83" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. I, 3, 83</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>I would play Lord P. of Phrygia,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tn 3.1.58" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. III, 1, 58</bibl></cit>. Alluded to in <bibl n="shak. aww 2.1.100" default="NO" valid="yes">All's II, 1, 100</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>